---
title: Mozzarella & Mushroom Hoagies with Dijon Mayo & Seasoned Potato Wedges
description: This week, a classic sandwich gets a veggie-centric twist, and we’ve gotta say—we don’t miss the beef at all. Meaty mushrooms are sautéed with bold and savory steak spices til they’re crispy and caramelized. Then, they’re stuffed into toasted baguettes, along with a creamy Dijon mayo, a tangle of peppers and onions, and a blanket of gooey mozz. One bite will have you feeling like Rocky after he ran up all those stairs—but better, because *you* have a sandwich!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/60e5baa047bafc0131290e93-19c3f9ac.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/mozzarella-mushroom-hoagies-60e5baa047bafc0131290e93-3f82b052.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mozzarella-mushroom-hoagies-60e5baa047bafc0131290e93
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 950 kcal
